## âš™ï¸ **2ï¸âƒ£ Download & Compile DAQ**

```bash
sudo mkdir -p /usr/src/snort_src
# Place `daq-2.0.7.tar.gz` in `/usr/src/snort_src` (optional)
cd /usr/src/snort_src
